OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers will
OL,6,Fcontinue through the evening,
OL,7,Fgenerally becoming light and more
OL,8,Fisolated although the Pennines likely
OL,9,Fstill seeing some heavier bursts.
OL,10,FShowers easing off into the early
OL,11,Fhours with some clear spells
OL,12,Fdeveloping and feeling cold. Light
OL,13,Fwinds.
OL,14,
OL,15,CMonday:FSunny spells and occasional
OL,16,Fshowers through the day, some of which
OL,17,Fcould be heavy and thundery. Clouding
OL,18,Fover from the west overnight as rain
OL,19,Fand stronger winds arrive.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
