OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FTuesday breezy with early rain turning
OL,7,Fto frequent heavy showers. Wednesday
OL,8,Fbreezy with showers. Becoming more
OL,9,Fsettled on Thursday with only the odd
OL,10,Fisolated shower. Temperatures near
OL,11,Faverage, trending upwards.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
